<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Study Village</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
</head>
<body class="village-bg">
  <section class="hero">
    <h1 class="hero-title"><span class="accent">Study Village</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">공부 마을</p>
    <p class="hero-tagline">
      친구들과 같은 방에서 공부하고, 집중한 시간만큼 알을 부화시켜<br />
      나만의 캐릭터를 도감에 모아보세요.
    </p>

    <div class="hero-sprites">
      <img src="/images/characters/c1.png" alt="말랑이" />
      <img src="/images/characters/c2.png" alt="동글이" />
      <img src="/images/characters/c3.png" alt="별마법사" />
      <img src="/images/characters/c4.png" alt="강철기사" />
      <img src="/images/characters/c5.png" alt="불꽃마왕" />
    </div>

    <% if (currentUser) { %>
      <p class="hero-welcome"><%= currentUser.nickname %>님, 어서 오세요!</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/room" class="hero-btn primary">학습방 입장</a>
        <a href="/records" class="hero-btn secondary">내 기록</a>
        <a href="/characters" class="hero-btn secondary">내 도감</a>
      </div>
      <div>
        <a href="/auth/logout" class="hint" style="display:inline-block;margin-top:16px;">로그아웃</a>
        <form action="/auth/withdraw" method="POST"
              onsubmit="return confirm('정말로 탈퇴하시겠습니까? 모든 정보가 삭제됩니다.');"
              style="display:inline;">
          <button type="submit" class="hero-withdraw">회원탈퇴</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    <% } else { %>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/auth/login" class="hero-btn primary">로그인</a>
        <a href="/auth/register" class="hero-btn secondary">회원가입</a>
      </div>
    <% } %>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
